## Meta-insight

Writing Cursor rules is itself context engineering! You're deciding:
- What memory should always be present
- What can be retrieved on-demand
- How to structure instructions for optimal AI behavior

The same tradeoffs apply to any AI product (like Manifest's shopping assistant).
